Class BaseEventDelayHandler.ReEvent

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.sakaiproject.content.providers.BaseEventDelayHandler.ReEvent
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Event
    Enclosing class:
    BaseEventDelayHandler

    protected static class BaseEventDelayHandler.ReEvent
extends Object
implements Event
    Local implementation of Event to allow the setting of all fields when refiring an event after it has been scheduled to run later than it was originally fired.
